<view class="page tier-template-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">公里阶梯价模板</view><view class="form-header-desc">小板和代驾线路可根据运送公里数设置分段阶梯价，便于系统精确报价。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">新建价格模板</view><view class="field"><text class="label">适用线路类型 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="grid-two"><view class="{{['check-row', b && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{c}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{a}}</text><text>小板线路</text></view><view class="{{['check-row', e && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{f}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{d}}</text><text>代驾线路</text></view></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">模板名称 <text class="required">*</text></text><input class="input" placeholder="例如: 华东近郊阶梯报价" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{g}}" bindinput="{{h}}"/></view><view class="field"><view class="row-between align-center" style="margin-bottom:12rpx"><text class="label" style="margin-bottom:0">分段阶梯规则 <text class="required">*</text></text><button class="add-tier-btn" size="mini" bindtap="{{i}}">+ 新增区间</button></view><view wx:for="{{j}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="k" class="tier-rule-row"><view class="tier-rule-head"><text class="tier-rule-title">段 {{item.a}}</text><button class="tier-delete-btn" size="mini" bindtap="{{item.b}}">删除</button></view><view class="tier-range-line"><view class="tier-input-box"><input class="input tier-input" type="number" placeholder="起始" bindinput="{{item.c}}" value="{{item.d}}"/><text class="tier-unit">KM</text></view><text class="tier-connector">至</text><view class="tier-input-box"><text class="tier-prefix wide">小于</text><input class="input tier-input" type="number" placeholder="{{item.e}}" bindinput="{{item.f}}" value="{{item.g}}"/><text class="tier-unit">KM</text></view></view><view class="tier-price-line"><text class="tier-price-label">单价</text><input class="input price-input-mini" type="digit" placeholder="请输入每公里价格" value="{{item.h}}" bindinput="{{item.i}}"/><text class="unit-txt">元/KM</text></view><view class="tier-rule-hint">{{item.j}}</view></view></view><view class="template-form-footer"><button class="primary-btn animate-btn w-full" loading="{{k}}" bindtap="{{l}}"> 保存并添加价格模板 </button></view></view><view class="section" style="margin-top:30rpx"><view class="section-title">已有价格模板 ({{m}})</view><view wx:if="{{n}}" class="empty"> 暂无已保存的阶梯价模板 </view><view wx:else class="templates-list"><view wx:for="{{o}}" wx:for-item="t" wx:key="g" class="template-item-card"><view class="template-head"><view><view class="template-name font-bold">{{t.a}}</view><view class="template-type">{{t.b}}</view></view><button class="delete-template-btn" size="mini" loading="{{t.c}}" bindtap="{{t.d}}"> 删除 </button></view><view class="template-rules-summary"><view wx:if="{{t.e}}" class="rule-summary-row"> 暂无计费规则 </view><view wx:for="{{t.f}}" wx:for-item="rule" wx:key="c" class="rule-summary-row">{{rule.a}}： <text class="price-hl font-bold">{{rule.b}}元/公里</text></view></view></view></view></view><miniapp-login-sheet class="r" u-r="loginSheet" bindsuccess="{{q}}" u-i="2e6822d2-0" bind:__l="__l"/></view>